        <abstract>
            <p>Congratulates AG on the "grand news of Richmond".</p>
            <p>Still interested in dimorphism and would welcome new cases.</p> 
<p>Working on <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi></p>  
<p>and correcting proofs of <hi rend="italic">Climbing plants</hi>.</p>  
<p>Would like seed of AG’s dimorphic <hi rend="italic">Plantago</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Cannot understand how the wind could fertilise reciprocally dimorphic flowers.</p>
        </abstract>
